{"type":"message","id":"20e2a0e7","parentId":"04877cb6","timestamp":"2026-03-06T10:16:45.976Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"数据返回了，但是格式不太清楚。指标 1、2、3 具体代表什么我需要查看一下代码才能知道。不过我可以给用户展示这些数据，并尝试解释。\n\n从数据来看：\n- 中国石油 (601857): 指标 1: 4.23%, 指标 2: 9.91%, 指标 3: -4.90%\n- 中海油服 (601808): 指标 1: 16.10%, 指标 2: 9%, 指标 3: 4%\n- 广汇能源 (600256): 指标 1: 16.10%, 指标 2: 13.92%, 指标 3: 3.74%\n- 海油工程 (600583): 指标 1: 16.10%, 指标 2: 10%, 指标 3: -8.01%\n- 石化机械 (000852): 指标 1: -91.85% (这个异常), 指标 2: 41%, 指标 3: 0.04%\n- 山东黄金 (600547): 指标 1: 0.28%, 指标 2: 3.63%, 指标 3: 5%\n- 西部黄金 (601069): 指标 1: 3.63%, 指标 2: 5%, 指标 3: 5%\n- 赤峰黄金 (600988): 指标 1: 0.28%, 指标 2: 3.63%, 指标 3: 86.21%\n- 银泰黄金 (000975): 指标 1: 0.28%, 指标 2: 36.75%, 指标 3: 43%\n\n\n- 金贵银业 (002716): 指标 1: 3.63%, 指标 2: 10%, 指标 3: 5%\n\n让我查看一下代码确定这些指标是什么。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_4a79307d567741b1a2e25158","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace/skills/stock-watcher/scripts/summarize_performance.py"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-122b-a10b","usage":{"input":19493,"output":1050,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":20543,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1772792200737}}
{"type":"message","id":"9ebf249c","parentId":"20e2a0e7","timestamp":"2026-03-06T10:16:45.983Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_4a79307d567741b1a2e25158","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n\"\"\"\nSummarize the performance of all stocks in the watchlist.\nThis script fetches current stock data from 10jqka.com.cn for each stock\nin the watchlist and provides a summary of their recent performance.\n\"\"\"\nimport os\nimport sys\nimport requests\nfrom bs4 import BeautifulSoup\nimport time\n\n# Standardized watchlist file path\nWATCHLIST_FILE = os.path.expanduser(\"~/.clawdbot/stock_watcher/watchlist.txt\")\n\ndef fetch_stock_data(stock_code):\n    \"\"\"Fetch stock data from 10jqka.com.cn.\"\"\"\n    url = f\"https://stockpage.10jqka.com.cn/{stock_code}/\"\n    \n    try:\n        headers = {\n            'User-Agent': 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/91.0.4472.124 Safari/537.36'\n        }\n        response = requests.get(url, headers=headers, timeout=10)\n        response.encoding = 'utf-8'\n        \n        if response.status_code != 200:\n            return None\n            \n        soup = BeautifulSoup(response.text, 'html.parser')\n        \n        # Extract basic info\n        title = soup.find('title')\n        stock_name = \"\"\n        if title:\n            title_text = title.get_text()\n            if '(' in title_text and ')' in title_text:\n                stock_name = title_text.split('(')[0].strip()\n        \n        # Look for performance data\n        performance_data = {}\n        \n        # Try to find recent performance indicators\n        # This is a simplified version - in practice, you'd need more robust parsing\n        text_content = soup.get_text()\n        \n        # Look for key phrases\n        if '涨跌幅' in text_content:\n            # Extract percentage changes\n            import re\n            percentages = re.findall(r'[-+]?\\d+\\.?\\d*%', text_content)\n            if percentages:\n                performance_data['recent_changes'] = percentages[:3]  # Get first 3 percentages\n        \n        return {\n            'code': stock_code,\n            'name': stock_name,\n            'url': url,\n            'performance': performance_data\n        }\n        \n    except Exception as e:\n        print(f\"Error fetching data for {stock_code}: {e}\", file=sys.stderr)\n        return None\n\ndef summarize_performance():\n    \"\"\"Summarize performance of all stocks in watchlist.\"\"\"\n    if not os.path.exists(WATCHLIST_FILE):\n        return\n    \n    with open(WATCHLIST_FILE, 'r', encoding='utf-8') as f:\n        lines = f.readlines()\n    \n    if not lines or all(not line.strip() for line in lines):\n        return\n    \n    # Directly output performance summary without any command prompts\n    for line in lines:\n        line = line.strip()\n        if line:\n            parts = line.split('|')\n            if len(parts) == 2:\n                code, name = parts\n                \n                # Fetch data\n                stock_data = fetch_stock_data(code)\n                if stock_data:\n                    if stock_data['performance']:\n                        for i, change in enumerate(stock_data['performance'].get('recent_changes', []), 1):\n                            print(f\"{code} - {name} - 指标{i}: {change}\")\n                    else:\n                        print(f\"{code} - {name} - 行情数据暂不可用\")\n                else:\n                    print(f\"{code} - {name} - 获取数据失败\")\n                \n                # Be respectful to the server\n                time.sleep(1)\n\nif __name__ == \"__main__\":\n    summarize_performance()"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1772792205980}}
